sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User Browser
    participant Gateway as data-science-gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.3
    participant HTTPRoute as HTTPRoute<br/>/mlflow prefix
    participant MLflowSvc as MLflow Service<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.3
    participant MLflowPod as MLflow Server Pod<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.3
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant DB as PostgreSQL<br/>5432/TCP TLS1.2+

    Note over User,DB: Flow 1: User Access to MLflow via Gateway

    User->>Gateway: GET /mlflow/...<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (K8s)
    Gateway->>HTTPRoute: Route via HTTPRoute config
    HTTPRoute->>MLflowSvc: Forward HTTPS/8443<br/>Bearer Token
    MLflowSvc->>MLflowPod: Forward HTTPS/8443<br/>Bearer Token
    MLflowPod->>K8sAPI: self_subject_access_review<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>MLflowPod: Authorization Result
    MLflowPod-->>MLflowSvc: HTTP Response
    MLflowSvc-->>Gateway: HTTP Response
    Gateway-->>User: JSON/HTML Response

    Note over User,DB: Flow 2: MLflow Experiment Tracking

    User->>MLflowPod: POST /api/2.0/mlflow/runs/create<br/>Bearer Token
    MLflowPod->>K8sAPI: Verify Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>MLflowPod: Token Valid
    MLflowPod->>DB: INSERT experiment metadata<br/>Username/Password
    DB-->>MLflowPod: Success
    MLflowPod->>S3: PUT artifact data<br/>AWS IAM/Access Keys
    S3-->>MLflowPod: Upload Complete
    MLflowPod-->>User: Run Created (ID)

    Note over User,DB: Flow 3: Operator Reconciliation

    participant OpPod as Operator Pod
    participant Helm as Helm Chart Engine

    OpPod->>K8sAPI: Watch MLflow CRs<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>OpPod: MLflow CR Created/Updated
    OpPod->>Helm: Render templates with CR values
    Helm-->>OpPod: Kubernetes manifests
    OpPod->>K8sAPI: Apply manifests<br/>(Deployment, Service, etc)
    K8sAPI-->>OpPod: Resources created/updated
    OpPod->>K8sAPI: Create HTTPRoute
    K8sAPI-->>OpPod: HTTPRoute created
    OpPod->>K8sAPI: Create ConsoleLink
    K8sAPI-->>OpPod: ConsoleLink created

    Note over User,DB: Flow 4: Prometheus Metrics Collection

    participant Prom as Prometheus

    Prom->>OpPod: GET /metrics (8443/HTTPS)<br/>Bearer Token
    OpPod-->>Prom: Prometheus metrics
